Name: Getting list of heroes without internet and cache
Preconditions: first installment, internet is turned off
Steps:
1. Open app
No internet connection error and button "Try again" are shown
2. Press button "Try again"
No internet connection error and button "Try again" are shown
3. Turn internet on and press button "Try again"
List of heroes is shown after loading

Name: Getting list of heroes with internet and without cache
Preconditions: first installment, internet is turned on
Steps:
1.Open app
List of heroes is shown after loading

Name: Getting list of heroes without internet and with cache
Preconditions: get list of heroes in previous sessions
Steps:
1.Open app
List of heroes is shown without loading

